hadiths[19]{hadithnumber,text}:
2070,"Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne Abdullah-bin abi-Bakr se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Ibad bin Tameem se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zaid Mazni (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Madina se) bahar nikal kar eidgaah gaey, barish mangi aur jab aap qibla rukh huey to aapni chadar ko palta."
2071,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Abdullah-bin abi-Bakr se, unhon-ne Ibad bin Tameem se aur unhon-ne apne chacha ( Abdullah-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Madina se) nikal kar eidgaah tashrif le gaey aur barish ki dua ki, aap ne qibley ki taraf rukh kya, apni chadar paltii aur 2 rakaat Namaz padhi."
2072,"abu-Bakar-bin Muhammad-bin Amr ne bataya ke unko Ibad bin Tameem ne khabar di, unko Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zaid Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) barish ki dua karne ke liye eidgaah gaey aur jab aap ne dua karne ka irada farmaya to qible ki taraf rukh kar liya aur apni chadar ko palat diya."
2073,"ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Ibad bin Tameem Mazni ne khabar di, unhon-ne apne chacha se suna aur wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon mein se they wo keh rahe they : aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) barish ki dua mangney ke liye nikley, Allah se dua kartey huey apni pusht logon ki taraf ki, munh qible ki taraf kya aur apni chadar palti, phir 2 rakaat Namaz ada ki."
2074,"Shoba ne Sabit se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap dua ke liye donon hath uthatey yahan tak ke aap ki baghlon ki safedi nazar aati thi."
2075,Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Sabit se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne barish maangney ke liye dua farmai to apne hathon ki pusht ke sath aasman ki taraf ishara kya.
2076,"ibne-abi Adi aur Abdul-Aala ne Saeed (bin abi-Aruba ( se, unhon-ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) istisqa (baarish k barasney ki dua) ke siwa kisi aur dua ke liye apne hath ( itney zyada ( buland nahi kartey they. yahan tak ke us se aap ki baghlon ki safedi dikhai diye lagti , albatta Abdul-Aala ne ( shak ke saath) kaha (يري بياض ابطه اوبياض ابطيه) (aap ki baghl ki safedi ya donon baghlon ki safedi dikhai diye lagti.)"
2077,Yahya-bin-Saeed ne ( Saeed (bin abi-Aruba se aur unhon-ne Qatada se riwayat ki ke unko Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi (pichhli hadis) ke ham mana hadis bayan ki.
2078,"Sharik bin abi namr ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Jumey ke roz aik aadmi us darwazey se masjid mein dakhil hua jo daarul-qaza ki taraf tha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey khutba irshad farma rahe they, us ne khadey khadey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf rukh kya, phir kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! maal maweshi halaak ho gaey aur rastey kat chukey, Allah Taala se dua farmaein ke wo hamein barish ata kare. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon hath utha diye, phir kaha : aey Allah ! hamein barish inayat farma, aey Allah ! hamein barish inayat farma, aey Allah ! hamein barish se nawaz de. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ham aasman mein na koi ghata dekh rahe they aur na badal ka koi tukda . hamarey aur Sala pahaad ke darmyan koi ghar tha na mohalla. phir iske peechhey se dhaal jaisi chhoti si badli uthi, jab wo aasman ke beech mein pahunchi to phail gaee, phir wo barsi, Allah ki qasam! ham ne hafta bhar suraj na dekha. phir agley Jumey usi darwazey se aik aadmi dakhil hua, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey khutba irshad farma rahe they, us ne khadey khadey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf rukh karke kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ( barish ki kasarat se) maal maweshi halaak ho gaey aur rastey band ho gaey, isliye Allah Taala se dua farmaein ke wo ham se barish rok ley. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne donon hath utha diye, phir farmaya : aey Allah! hamarey ird-gird (barish barsa) ham par nahi, aey Allah! pahaadiyon par, teelon par, wadiyon ke andar (nadiyon mein) aur darakht ugney ke maqamat par (barsa.) kaha : (fauran) badal chhat gaey aur ham (masjid se) nikley to dhoop mein chal rahe they. Sharik ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya wo pahley wala aadmi tha? unhon-ne jawab diya : main nahi janta."
2079,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein logon ko khushk sali ne aa liya. usi beech mein ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jumey ke din member par logon ke samney khutba de rahe they ke achcha aik badwi khada hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool : maal maweshi halaak ho gaey, baal bachchey bhookey marney lagey. (aagey) usi (pichhli hadis) ke ham mana hadis bayan ki. aur is mein hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah! hamarey ird-gird ( barsa ( hamarey uper nahi. kaha : aur aap apne hath se jis taraf bhi ishara kartey they usi taraf se badal chhat jatey they yahan tak ke maine Madina Munawra ko) zamin ke) khali tukdey ki tarah dekha aur wadi qana aik maah tak behti rahi aur kisi taraf se bhi koi shakhs nahi aaya magar us ne musladhar barish ki khabar di."
2080,"Abdul-Aala bin Hammad aur Muhammad-bin abi-Bakr muqaddami ne kaha : hamein Motamir ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Sabit Bunani se aur unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jumey ke din khutba de rahe they ke log aap ke samney khadey ho gaey, ( baat shuru karne waley baddoo ke sath doosrey bhi shamil ho gaey ( wo faryaad karne lagey aur kehney lagey : aey Allah ke Nabi ! barish band ho gayi , darakhton (ke pattey sookh kar) surkh ho gaey aur maweshi halak ho gaey. aur (aagey uper zikr ki gaee hadis ki tarah) hadis bayan ki. usmein Abdul-Aala ki riwayat se ye (alfaz) hain : Madina se badal chhat gaey aur uske ird-gird barish barsney lagi jabke Madina mein aik qatra bhi nahi baras raha tha maine Madina ko dekha wo aik tarah ke taaj ke andar ( barish se mehfooz ( tha."
2081,Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne Sabit aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se usi ke ham mana riwayat ki aur ye izafa kya : Allah Taala ne badalon ko jod diya aur ham usi ( haalat ( mein rahe yahan tak ke maine dekha aik qawii aur mazbut aadmi ko bhi iska dil ( barish ki kasarat ki bina par) us fikr mein mubtala kar deta tha ke wo apne ahal w ayaal ke paas pahunchey .
2082,"Hafs bin Ubaidullah bin Anas-bin-Malik ne bayan kya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Jumey ke din aik dehati Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya jabke aap member par they. ( aagey mazkura (uper zikr) hadees ki tarah ( hadis bayan ki aur is mein ye izafa kya : maine badal ko dekha wo is tarah chhat raha tha jaisey wo aik badi chadar ho jab usey lapeta ja raha ho."
2083,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they ke ham par barish barasney lagi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna ( sar aur kandhey ka kapda ( khol diya yahan tak ke barish aap par aaney lagi ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap ne aisa kyon kiya? aap ne farmaya : kyonke wo nai-nai ( seedhi ( apne rab azz-w-jall ki taraf se aa rahi hai.
2084,"Jafar bin-Muhammad ne Ata-bin-abi-Ribah se riwayat ki unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aadat mubaraka thi ke jab aandhi ya badal ka din hota to aap ke chehra Mubarak par iska asar pehchaana ja sakta tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( iztirab ke aalim mein) kabhi aagey jatey aur kabhi peechhey hattey , phir jab barish barasnaa shuru ho jati to aap us se khush ho jatey aur wo ( pehli kaifiyat) aap se door ho jaati, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine (eik baar (aap se (uski wajah) puchha to aap ne farmaya : main dar gaya ke ye azab na ho jo meri ummat par musallat kar diya gaya ho aur barish ko dekh letey to farmatey rehmat hai."
2085,"ibne-Juraij, Ata-bin-abi-Ribah se hadis bayan kartey hain, unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : jab tez hawa chaltii to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey : aey Allah ! main tujh se uski khair aur bhalai ka sawal karta hun aur jo usmein hai. uski aur jo kuchh iske zariey bheja gaya hai uski khair (ka talabgaar hon (aur uske shar se aur jo kuchh usmein hai aur jo usmein bheja gaya hai iske shar se teri panah chahta hun. (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : jab aasman par badal ghir aatey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka rang badal jata aur aap ( iztiraab (becheinii) ke aalim mein) kabhi bahar nikaltey aur kabhi andar aatey , kabhi aagey badhtey aur kabhi peechhey hat'tey , iske baad jab barish barasney lagti to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (ye kaifiyat ( door ho jaatii, mujhey us kaifiyat ka pata chal gaya, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Aaisha ! ho sakta hai (ye isi tarah ho ( jaisey qaum aad ne ( badalon ko dekh kar) kaha tha : jab unhon-ne us ( azab ( ko badal ki tarah apni bastiyon ki taraf aatey dekha to unhon-ne kaha : ye badal hai jo ham par barsey ga ."
2086,"Sulaiman-bin-Yasar ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : maine Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kabhi poori tarah aisa hanstaa huaa nahi dekha ke main aap ke halaq Mubarak ke andar ka ubhraa hua hissey dekh loon. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sirf muskuraayaa kartey they. aur jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) badal ya aandhii dekhtey to uska asar aap ke chehra anwar par bayaan ho jata. to (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main logon ko dekhti hon ke jab badal dekhtey hain to is ummeed par khush ho jatey hain ke usmein barish hogi aur main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekhti hon ke jab aap is ( badal ( dekhtey hain to main aap ke chehrey par na-pasandidgi mehsus karti hon ? Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Aaisha ! mujhey is baat se kya cheez amn dila sakti hai ke kahin unmein azab ( na ( ho, aik qaum aandhii ke azab ka shikar hui thi aur aik qaum ne azab ko) door) se dekha to kaha : ye badal hai jo ham par barish barsaey ga ."
2087,"Mujahid ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : baade-Sabaa ( mashriqii samt se chalney wali hawa) se meri madad ki gaee hai. aur) maghribii samt se chalney wali hawa) se qaume-aad ko halaak kiya gaya."
2088,Saeed-bin-Jubair ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uski manind (tarah) riwayat ki.
